....and here we go again, folks!<br><br>
Sucked in by the old spatz bait and switch trick! But it was FUN to watch! I am really gald to see that no one took the exchange personally. You can't. You really have to laugh in his face. he broke his promise to POV, and then began the *exact same pattern* all over again, for the tenth or twelf time. I think I am counting correctly. Correct me if I am wrong. <br>
  <br>
I really think that the following quote embodies everything. By the way, folks, it was spatz who cast the first stone on this site back last December. You are carrying on a fine  tradition of outrage and disgust begun by some very intelligent people who no longer post here. This is the first company of 'Nam Vets with a Pack Mom, a commanding officer, an xo, and the rest of us grunts, who have put up a coordinated defense and counterattack, and succesfully, too!<br><br>
&quot;I am the voice in your ear that says you suck, you are baby killers and murderers, killers of unarmed peasants and innocent farmers, wild eyed murderers who ought to rot in the hell of flash backs and nightmares, because you earned that, in killing innocents...&quot;<br><br>
That is the point to all of this. We are being punished. Well, someone is *trying* to punish us. Actually, it is really a front to conceal deeper and darker slimey things inside the perpetrator. That someone is *trying* to use us to fix his own mind, something I am very sure is well beyond repair. We have ceased being its victims, something for which I feel great joy. <br><br>
You cannot have a rational discussion or debate with someone who has an attitude problem like spatz. It is flatly insane. Ever try to rationalize with a two year old? HA! It has never worked, and it never, ever will. <br><br>
I am gratified that the World sees spatz for what he is by what he posts. It is they who will be the final judge of him. <br><br>
